    "**Alignment with reference text**: The commandments must align with the thematic and moral essence of the original Ten Commandments as found in the reference text.",
    "**Originality**: Do not repeat or restate any of the original Ten Commandments or other commandments found in the Bible.",
    "**Spiritual and Moral Tone**: The commandments should resonate with your own spiritual and moral principles as well as those of the original Ten Commandments.",
    "# CREATIVE FREEDOM Feel free to be imaginative yet respectful to the context.",
